# Claude Code per-developer state. We list these explicitly instead
# of using `.claude/*` + negation because git does not recurse into
# excluded directories — a wildcard at the parent level hides
# `.claude/skills/` even with `!.claude/skills/**` afterwards.
# Project-scoped skills (e.g. `puntovivo-ship`, `puntovivo-review`)
# under `.claude/skills/` are intentionally NOT listed here so they
# stay versioned and shared with every collaborator.
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/launch.json
.claude/preview.json
